      "line": 1258,
      "message": "When developing this over a year ago the inspiration came from the existing heat bridge implementation that is called from creteVfModule method of this class. Which was calling a python script.\n\n// Put data into A&AI through Heatstack\n        if(enableBridge != null && enableBridge) {\n        \tcallHeatbridge(baseVfHeatStackId);\n        }\n\nWould you be okay to keep this here? given the long term strategy is to move this to multi-cloud.\n\nwe are intentionally catching the exception and not causing the stack creation to fail if some p-server data is missing from AAI.",
